==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: grease-gun
<hw>grease-gun</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
device held in the hand, having a supply of grease and attached to a
reservoir of pressurized air, used to force grease between adjacent
moving parts of a machine, especially in the bearings of motor
vehicles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

